thread.title: Korean Chung pulls out of race for FIFA presidency
thread.title_full: Korean Chung pulls out of race for FIFA presidency | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Korean Chung pulls out of race for FIFA presidency
text:
ZURICH South Korea's Chung Mong-Joon on Monday pulled out of the race for the presidency of global soccer body FIFA due to a ban from the sport.
"Because of the ethics committee's unjust sanctions, I will have to miss the Oct. 26 deadline to file my candidacy," Chung said in a statement.
"It is now time to officially withdraw my candidacy for the next FIFA president."
(Reporting by Joshua Franklin ; Editing by Michael Shields )
